description:
Come join us for our second Equitech Tuesday event with Upsurge at Reveille Grounds. Other members of Baltimores tech scene will be there like The Maryland Technology Internship Program, Johns Hopkins Carey Business School & Bmore Collab.

We'll have empanadas and other refreshments, See you there!

HOW TO FIND US/ PARKING:

Street parking is free, plentiful, and unrestricted on Severn, Bush, and Bayard Streets, especially after 3:30pm and on weekends:
The code for the walk-in gate to the Courtyard is 0250#

Once through the gate, Building C is the first building on your left, and Reveille is on the 2nd Floor. To get there, you can either:
- Proceed ahead and take the external stairs on your left OR
- Use the wooden doors on your left to access the elevator (if locked, the code is also 0250#)

Gated parking is available on Bush Street & unrestricted on weekends:
If using your GPS, we recommend using 1799 Bush Street.
The black drive-in gate is on your left, and the code is 05230.
Proceed to the right, past the first set of spots on your left, and park in the spaces closest to the courtyard (past the first building on your left).

See the venue website (https://www.reveillegrounds.com/location) for more information.
